Drachma grabbed his club, and raised him self. The Ache, his curse, was still present but silenced itself. Drachma looked at the four rogues, and smirked, maybe they could show him death, the death he yearned for, the death he should have been given, by &quot;her&quot;.<br>
Drachma twirled the club deftly, as the Rogues charged him, he immediatly sent Whittlebonz to sit, and he took the charge. Drachma laughed as he killed the first, and took their backstabbs... Yes Lako(Halflings) kill me, kill me.<br>
Drachma grabbs annother of the Rogues, and bit into his flesh, blood dripped from his teeth. <br>
He clubbed annother that had begun to go after his pet, then as the last one saw the Ogur for what he was, a caged beast... a cursed monster, no longer caring for life. He ran, ran for his life, Drachma at his heels, Drachma cast disease cloud, the rogue still ran... Drachma began to speak an ancient form of Ogrish, lost by his Brethren,&quot; Hok Tark Piktok, tak h-takie, noron Distrof...&quot;<br>
(You have angered the ache , now Die)<br>
Drachma waved his hands about, and the Rogue, grasped his heart, and screamed in agony, he felt the pain, the Ache, he knew Drachma's pain, and died from it. Drachma held the rogues head.... &quot;Noron hok tik hak h-takie,&quot; as he tore the head off the Rogue's body. ( Now you know my ache)<br>
 Drachma sat back down, a tear in his eye.... my love, I will remember, and I'll be here.... &quot;Hok tae Hak Ratckie-N`ice,&quot;<br>
<br>
