Drachma came to a large building, it was empty, probably its last residence either moved to Norath or were killed long ago by some plague, either way, he was staying here. He sat down, and rooted through his pack, he grabbed the Rogues head, and took a bite, the skull cracked in one bite, blood streamed from his jaw, he drank deeply of all the rogues blood. he laid down and slept, dreaming of her, his Ratkie-N`ice.<br>
His muscles grew stiff during the night, the wind grew cold, and his ache again came, his roar was heard throughout the town, and all feared it, the sound of his anguish, the sound of him.<br>
Drachma leaned forward his arms supported by his knees, he coughed, he breathed deeply, but he felt like he was choking. Blood began to pour from his nose, as his heart, began to pump harder. <br>
Drachma fell forward, unconsious, his heart quieted, and his ache continued slightly...<br>
He woke up on the floor, a small Halfling sheriff kicked him, &quot;Get up, Ogre, get up.&quot;<br>
Drachma grabbed the foot and violently, hurled him to the floor, raising himself, he looked down at the terrified Halfling... &quot;What Do you want Lako,&quot;<br>
&quot;Ye best be leavin, my freinds are outside,&quot;<br>
&quot;Bah!!! Disturb the H-Takie, again, and you will die,&quot;<br>
Drachma grabbs his pack, and left what remained of the Rogues head, and left ShadowHaven....<br>
