<br>
the day came to night, and still he laid der, blood dried on his armor, and his wound scabbed over, the bone mending itself, ogur stamina and Zeks will having something to do with it.<br>
He awoke, and looked at the stars, the beauty there flooded his emotions and he wept, his feircnees flooded away as he wept, all the horrors, and sadness he had seen, was to much for him... he thought of Seraphimm, his love..how she had hurt him, he thought of what she had said to him last...<br>
&quot;Love is weak, and i can't be that weak again.&quot;<br>
He sighed to himself, he tried to change her mind, but to no avail, and now his love was killing him. It had made him stronger then he had ever been, but it was also torturing him. Looking up at the sky, he saw a cloud hover over him, he watched it for a moment, as the wind took it, and blew it away... that was him, that cloud, and the love was the wind... but he would not renounce his love of her. The love of Seraphimm, was greater then anything he had ever felt, he thought of her, and sighed... he laid down... and closed his eyes. He slept in peace, for once the pain went away for a while.<br>
<br>
Drachma awoke to the smell of flowers, he sniffed the smell, and he sighed thinking of seraphimm's perfume. He stood up, and picked up his pack, smelling the air, he became alert. he smelled Euridite, not only a eurdite but an Enchanter... he growled..his ache began to pump in his chest... his anger rose... he began to walk, sniffing the air.... searching for the enchanter... his father was killed by a Euridite enchanter, he hoped he would get lucky, and this would be the murderer... he came to the Euridite, killing a greenblood... he listened to what was said...<br>
&quot;what do you mean the son of Trach is searching for his fathers killers...&quot; said the Eurdite.<br>
&quot;Him say him kill eurdite... him angry about murder... him kill us.. him strong...him scare us.. he..ahhhhhhhh,&quot; screamed the Ogur as the enchanter tortured his cursed mind.<br>
&quot;you will tell him it was the Dwarfs wont you Ogur, tell him it was the Dwarf known as Dvalen..yes the Ogurs enemy.. that will be his fathers killer...&quot;<br>
Drachma began to breathe hard.. the ache..voiced its oppinion..kill...it said...kill now...<br>
Drachma burst from the hill.... &quot;All enemies of the mortal Zek shall fall&quot; <br>
the greenblood mesmorized jumped infront of Drachma..but he was easily slain.. the Eurdite casts every spell in his book..but nothing held... the ache was that strong.. Drachma grabbed the Eurdite... and bit into his flesh.. all in the mountains heard the scream of the enchanter... <br>
&quot;PLEASE... HELP ME... AHHHHHHHHHHH&quot;<br>
Drachma laughed.. a this moment he went for the moment insane.. and he enjoyed the Eurdites screams... as blood dripped from his jaw... he released the Eurdite.. the enchanter crawled..slowly stalked by the crazed Ogur. <br>
&quot;heheheheh... youm like killing my father..youm like me... killing you..hhehehehe... meet Zek...&quot;<br>
