as the days went by he still meditated..until the thrid night when he felt a hand... he felt his heart beat faster and a small trickle of blood fell from his lips...he turned and saw her... his seraphimm.<br>
She smiled at him, and he smiled back, his eyes filled with love, as he bowed to her.... <br>
&quot;M'lady.. it has been many a season since.....&quot; Drachma looked down, unable to finish...<br>
She touched his cheek... &quot;Im sorry...for hurting you..but i had to follow my destiny... my place is with my guild...and my......&quot;<br>
Drachma looked up, and he nodded, &quot;your husband... I have heard the tales...&quot; Drachma looked at her, still with the same love in his eyes... he kissed her hand... and held her hand to his cheek... <br>
&quot;I love you my goddess Seraphimm, if you ever need me I will come.. you are more immportant to me then Zek himself....and my club is yours.&quot;<br>
Drachma looked into her loving eyes... and he stood up.. he hugged her and kissed her upon the cheek... and departed with no further words.... <br>
<br>
Drachma looked back and saw her staring at him from the distance... he waved and blew a kiss to her... he turned back, and breathed a sigh as his heart began to pump back to normal... he relaxed his chest... and dropped to one knee... blood dripped out... he was glad she could not see him... and he was glad he had enough dicipline to stop the blood flow from entering his mouth... the grass steined red as the last dropp fell.... he breathed a sigh of releif... and made his way again.... He didn't know where to go... maybe planes of knwoledge... or Freeport...He knew he wanted to see Seraphimm again... maybe in the future he would be disiplined enough to over come the ache.... with the support of Seraphimm and his freinds he knew he would....<br>
