<br>
Days went by as the ship finnially pulled into Freeports dock....Drachma made his way out of the city not wishing to kill the gaurds that protected the humans....as he set foot outside into the surrounding land... he sat down beside a large cactus..and meditated..hours went by... and many young children waved at him... but Drachma did not move....days went by... and Drachma neither moved..and for along time..did not even breathe... as the 5 th day ended.... Drachma fell... blood dripped from his breast plate, but no wound he had....Drachma awoke... a vision he had...one of a seacret alliance between Zek and Tunare.... Tunare grinned at the Ogur in the vision..Drachma knew not why.... as he walked to East commomlands.... blood fell to the earth... seeping into the land....Drachma sat down His back sore.... so he took off the lage mithril.... and placed it upon the groung.... orcs, gathered around him... and fear grew in their eyes.... as blood seeped into Drachma's undershirt..creating an image.... a brand upon his skin.... Drachma turned around seeing the orcs..he grabbed his club... they bowed before him.... he looked at them..and saw a female goblin drawing..... the symbol of Zek...entwined with annother symbol....<br>
<br>
Drachma knowing something was different about that goblin....<br>
 &quot;what is that, speak!&quot;<br>
the goblin looked upon him with sadness.... and pointed at him....<br>
 &quot;You,&quot; she said<br>
&quot;Me?.... I am not that symbol.... you orcs and goblins are strange creature....&quot;<br>
the goblin looked at him..and made her way behind him... she touched the brand..and Drachma fell... almost unconsious... he knew not how...as the goblin touched the brand again.. his head fell to the ground.... he was nearly dead.....&quot;But h-o-w.... ugh...&quot;<br>
